19:55.960 --> 19:57.960
KONOSUBA!

19:56.950 --> 19:59.550
I would love to spar with you—

19:57.960 --> 20:00.460
Darkness!

20:00.460 --> 20:02.200
Darkness!

20:02.200 --> 20:03.940
Oh, good timing, Claire.

20:03.940 --> 20:05.720
Wh-What is it?

20:05.720 --> 20:09.730
I heard there's some kind of noble thief 
hassling the nobles around the capital?

20:09.730 --> 20:11.530
Th-That is true.

20:11.530 --> 20:14.980
Nobles with bad reputations 
do seem to be under fire.

20:14.980 --> 20:19.240
Well, I'm gonna nab this 
so-called noble thief!

20:19.240 --> 20:20.140
Huh?

20:20.610 --> 20:24.590
The thief no one has secured 
any leads on whatsoever?

20:24.590 --> 20:27.140
Just who is that seedy-looking fellow?

20:27.140 --> 20:30.470
He's not very remarkable. Some associate 
of Lady Dustiness, I think...

20:28.250 --> 20:31.240
<i>Uh, noble folks? I can hear you.</i>

20:31.240 --> 20:35.450
I don't care how good his intentions are! 
Theft is still theft! I can't just ignore that!

20:35.450 --> 20:38.330
Justice has never been near the top of your 
priorities before. What brought this on?

20:38.330 --> 20:41.000
I'm going to stay behind 
in order to protect everyone!

20:41.000 --> 20:43.450
You are unbelievable!

20:43.450 --> 20:45.010
Magnificent!

20:45.010 --> 20:48.000
Just as I would expect of 
Lady Dustiness's comrade!

20:48.000 --> 20:53.090
Not that I've personally done anything to 
earn the noble thief's ire, mind you...

20:53.090 --> 20:56.060
Likewise! I've done nothing 
wrong, I assure you!

20:56.060 --> 20:59.210
No, not a single thing that 
would paint a target on me...

20:58.140 --> 21:00.620
<i>These guys couldn't be more obvious.</i>

21:02.640 --> 21:04.440
<i>Oh, I see, I see!</i>

21:04.440 --> 21:08.060
<i>You can't wait to see your beloved 
elder brother in action, huh?!</i>

21:08.060 --> 21:10.350
<i>Leave it to me!</i>

21:10.350 --> 21:13.590
<i>I'll laze around the castle a bit more, 
and eventually catch this guy!</i>

21:13.590 --> 21:16.850
We're counting on you, unremarkable lad!

21:16.290 --> 21:18.580
I always knew he had it in him!

21:18.580 --> 21:22.430
Hurry and catch this rogue 
so we can all rest easy!

21:22.810 --> 21:26.430
Wait, what's up? We get to keep 
eating tasty food here tomorrow?

21:26.430 --> 21:31.050
Very well, then! It seems I'll need to 
save plenty of room for tomorrow's meal!

21:31.480 --> 21:34.280
What are you two saying?!

21:34.280 --> 21:35.720
Very well, then.

21:36.070 --> 21:39.990
Sir Kazuma will be stationed at 
the residences of likely targets

21:39.990 --> 21:42.120
in an effort to catch the thief.

21:43.840 --> 21:47.240
I ask you all to fully cooperate 
with him in his search!

21:56.890 --> 22:00.010
Damn it! This is not what I wanted!

23:30.010 --> 23:40.010
I'm touching you on purpose! I'm touching you on purpose.
