the Growth Chimera, Sylvia. The climate here is wonderful.
 It's almost like being on a long vacation.
 Thinking back, I worked non-stop without taking any breaks.
 Maybe I was desperate to live up to people's expectations... no.
 I think I didn't want to be outdone by the men around me.
 I may have been too headstrong for my own good.
 From a house aside the bubbling waters of the River Styx, with love...
touching you on purpose.
-Sylvia

